description: Go wanted to catch as many Pokémon as he could and one day while in a forest in the Kanto region, he caught every Bug type Pokémon native to Kanto. Venomoth resides at a habitat at the Sakuragi Institute in Vermilion City. It is not the evolved form of Go`s Venonat as that is a separate Pokémon.
name: Morphon (Gou)
